<b>Applied impact assignment</b> identifies the item(s) affected resulting from 
<express_ref linkend="risk:arm:Risk_arm.Applied_risk_consequence"/>.  
<note number="1">The item impacted is typically intrinsic such as a transition in state of a product, 
