  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Risk_arm.Risk_perception">
<b>Risk perception</b> is a set of values or concerns with which a stakeholder views a particular risk.  
<note number="1">Risk perception depends on the stakeholder's expressed needs, issues, and knowledge.</note>
<note number="2">Risk perception can differ from objective data.</note>
</ext_description>
