   <express_ref linkend="risk:arm:Risk_arm.Risk_retention"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Risk_arm.Risk_retention">
<b>Risk retention</b> is an acceptance of the burden of loss, or benefit of gain, from a particular risk.
<note number="1">Risk retention includes the acceptance of risks that have not been identified</note>
<note number="2">Risk retention does not include treatments involving insurance, or transfer by other means.</note>
<note number="3">There can be variability in the degree of acceptance and dependence on risk criteria</note>

</ext_description>
