  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Risk_arm.Risk_transfer">
<b>Risk transfer</b> is the sharing with another party the benefit of gain, or burden of loss, for a particular risk.
<note number="1">Risk transfer may be carried out through insurance or other agreements.</note>
<note number="2">Risk transfer can create new risks or modify existing risk.</note>
<note number="3">Relocation of the source is not risk transfer.</note>
<note number="4">Legal or statutory requirements can limit, prohibit or mandate the transfer of certain risk.</note>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
