  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Risk_arm.Risk_treatment">
<b>Risk treatment</b> is the process of selection and implementation of measures to modify risk.
<note number="1">The term risk treatment is sometimes used for the measures themselves.</note>
<note number="2">Risk treatment measures can include avoiding, optimizing, transferring or retaining risk.</note>

</ext_description>
